articles.title: Another shockingly good jobs report shows America's economy is booming - CNN
articles.description: The US economy added a whopping 353,000 jobs last month, far more than the 176,500 jobs expected. It's yet another data point that underlines the country's economic strength, even in the face of 11 rate hikes from the Federal Reserve.
